{"tid":2026561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(戰鬥民族服) 透明保護衣配內衣褲  俄羅斯女護士遭紀律處分","createTime":"2020-05-21T04:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T06:40:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6b35bc9af385bd8b345953a45dadd3e5c6e3263a","tid":2026561,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200520/_2020052021550414663.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200520%2F_2020052021550414663.jpg&h=4b7705c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情持續，俄羅斯近日一間醫院的男病房出現一幕「奇景」。一名女護士身穿透明保護衣，而其裡面卻僅穿內衣褲去照顧男病人。有病人將照片上載到網絡，並說同房病人並無投訴，但確實有點尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該名女護士是工作於俄羅斯圖拉州某臨床醫院，從照片上看到女護士身著透明保護衣及內衣褲照顧病人。而該名護士其後解釋道，在保護衣下穿上制服太悶焗，才只穿內衣褲，且初時並不知道保護衣是那麼透明。但院方及當地衛生部門並不接納其解釋，以該護士未有遵守傳染病房穿衣規定，施以紀律處分及批評。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起網民熱論，部分網民支持該護士，指所有人都批評她，卻忽視她這樣穿著是因為太熱；甚至有網民表示她為病人帶來歡樂，認為這種穿衣風格，有利於培養病人的積極情緒，有利於病人早日康復。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1776445/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E9%80%8F%E6%98%8E%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E8%A1%A3%E9%85%8D%E5%85%A7%E8%A1%A3%E8%A4%B2-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%A5%B3%E8%AD%B7%E5%A3%AB%E9%81%AD%E7%B4%80%E5%BE%8B%E8%99%95%E5%88%86</code></pre>"},{"pid":"ee1f68ccd832d4c1421a2025c5211a09dae1dc57","tid":2026561,"uid":194142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:48:59.000Z","msg":"係日本發生就係另一件事"},{"pid":"7c076f581fa4e962112f15584d23acf8b2687500","tid":2026561,"uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4VqgjR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4VqgjR.png&h=2819a618&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fb94dfe4f2c700ac63fe7981c667c0fe1c1242a","tid":2026561,"uid":80484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:51:41.000Z","msg":"無人投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fcbde50be61ff42f8a653bd491868ef7b1c08d","tid":2026561,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7c076f581fa4e962112f15584d23acf8b2687500","tid":2026561,"uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4VqgjR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4VqgjR.png&h=2819a618&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:51:43.000Z","msg":"鼻涕柱男.jpg"},{"pid":"4fcae52e34e139db404243e0d3db02f41f4f1b8c","tid":2026561,"uid":191139,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"無人投訴都要被處分<br />\n<br />\n處分個個肯撚定係 人又醜 閪又臭嘅老姑婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f52b3de02fd10730924f827129a43c6d6af7c3","tid":2026561,"uid":192465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:03:06.000Z","msg":"護士：我想咁cosplay好耐"},{"pid":"88c361f2dcd693a2aef5fcbd48e7569c0e1e9767","tid":2026561,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:04:16.000Z","msg":"起碼身上多返啲肉色，似返個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2d00a54e9ad3c9ea86cae809ef8b7bdf276596","tid":2026561,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7c076f581fa4e962112f15584d23acf8b2687500","tid":2026561,"uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4VqgjR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4VqgjR.png&h=2819a618&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78083a468eff2ae0763599ea1187bfbf2a72953","tid":2026561,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime